_help_theme() {
    cat << 'EOF'
dotfiles theme — manage colour themes

USAGE
  dotfiles theme [SUBCOMMAND] [ARGS]
  dotfiles -t

SUBCOMMANDS
  list                 List available themes
  current              Show the current theme
  <name>               Switch to a named theme
