  delete <name>        Remove a generated theme

OPTIONS
  -h, --help     Show this help

EXAMPLES
  dotfiles theme list
  dotfiles theme current
  dotfiles theme dracula
  dotfiles theme generate zenburn
  dotfiles theme delete zenburn
